# Histograms for different set types in Squash App

### Who

<!--Who does this benefit or who will this affect? Who should be able to view this?-->

- Yamb players

### What

<!--What problem needs addressing?-->

- Currently, we have seen cases where a user has filled in the scoresheet and pressed submit. This directs them to the New Game page, where they need to submit again to record the match.
- We would like to make it so you can submit a New Game directly from a filled in scoresheet

### Why

<!--What value does this add?-->

- If a user forgets to submit again, we will be missing data, which is a shame. 

### Acceptance Criteria

